Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.31,0:19:27.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別太高興了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.07,0:19:30.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你剛才所做的不過是模仿空破斬罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.48,0:19:33.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
